readme.md

Awesome

     A curated list of services for static websites.

   Inspired by the [https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome]awesome list
   thing.

Table of Contents

     * Audio
     * Books
     * Calendar and Scheduling
     * Images
     * Maps
     * Presentations
     * Video
     * Code
     * Functions as a Service
